# Deployment Branch Policy

- Use `master` as the primary deployment branch for this project.
- When a user asks to publish to GitHub Pages, prefer updating and pushing `master`.
- Before pushing, verify local branch status and remote sync (`git status -sb`).
- Avoid publishing from `gh-pages` unless the user explicitly asks for that exception.
- If branch cleanup is requested, ask for explicit confirmation before deleting any branch.
